<p><i><b>Big Deal</b></i> is a <a href="Musical_theatre" title="Musical theatre">musical</a> with a book by <a href="Bob_Fosse" title="Bob Fosse">Bob Fosse</a> using songs from various composers such as <a href="Ray_Henderson" title="Ray Henderson">Ray Henderson</a>, <a href="Eubie_Blake" title="Eubie Blake">Eubie Blake</a>, and <a href="Jerome_Kern" title="Jerome Kern">Jerome Kern</a>. It was based on the film "Big Deal on Madonna Street" by <a href="Mario_Monicelli" title="Mario Monicelli">Mario Monicelli</a>. The musical received five <a href="Tony_Award" title="Tony Award">Tony Award</a> nominations, with Fosse winning for Choreography.</p>
